public interface SAttribute
extends SNamed, IValue, ITyped

A representation of the model object ' SAttribute'.

Author:
Miles Parker

The following features are supported:

  • Owner
  • Gather Data
  • Default Value
  • Units
  • Immutable
  • Derived
  • Children
